definitions.definition: A transliteration of the Ukrainian male given name Володи́мир ( Volodýmyr ) , equivalent to Vladimir .
A city and raion of Volyn Oblast, in western Ukraine .
Ukrainian form of Vladimir , a city , the administrative centre of Vladimir Oblast, Russia .
